<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-10-25T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-10-25T07:00:00-05:00" n="303" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d303">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/7442</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Special Agent in Corfu</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DHP1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Dodge</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Corfu</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-25T14:00:00+02:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">October 25, 1917, 2 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received October 26, 5.05
                                    a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Your September 28, 6 p.m.<note n="1" xml:id="d303fn1">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_214">p.
                                    214</ref>.</note> Departure Serbian mission delayed and now
                                tentatively fixed for about November 15. Composition will be
                                somewhat changed. Premier assures me that no representatives of the
                                Yugoslav Committee of London will visit the United States.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_DHP1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>